for i in range(1, 7):
    estimator = KMeans(n_clusters = i)
    ids = estimator.fit_predict(processed_data[['인구수', '물류창고 개수']])
    plt.subplot(3, 2, i)
    plt.tight_layout()
    plt.title("K value = {}".format(i))
    plt.xlabel('인구수')
    plt.ylabel('물류창고 개수')
    plt.scatter(processed_data['인구수'], processed_data['물류창고 개수'], c=ids, cmap='viridis')  
plt.show()
